Except as otherwise specifically provided for in this Charter, the terms of all Town Board members shall be for two years, and shall commence on the first Monday in July of 1999 and biennially thereafter. All Town Board members shall be eligible for reappointment and shall continue in office until a successor has been appointed and has qualified.